{"tid":1032540,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)冒險聖歌","createTime":"2019-02-22T12:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T12:06:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"673b8fe3e185612ee6ac3347a686ab0224c4e228","tid":1032540,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=96d76126\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=00e82cbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=6dd33722\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/news-image/6c6fafeeecb6b6dece7953952722895f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews-image%2F6c6fafeeecb6b6dece7953952722895f&h=432cf0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《冒險聖歌》是曾打造《質量效應》、《闇龍紀元》等系列的 BioWare 開發的科幻題材原創動作角色扮演遊戲，以被諸神「塑造者」所遺棄的未完成世界為舞台，玩家將深入這個蠻荒世界，以傭兵的身分承接各式任務，一邊對抗邪惡的「創痕」入侵，一邊探索塑造者遺留的謎題。遊戲中玩家將扮演「自由戰士」的成員，駕駛動力裝甲「標槍機甲」來進行任務，有各式各樣類型與特性的機甲可以選擇，還可以自訂裝備、武器與能力，透過連線與同好組成戰隊一同冒險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon